                <style>
                    .custom-checkbox {
                        width: 16px;

                        }

                        .custom-checkbox.selected {
                            /*background: url("/examples/images/checkbox-selected.png") no-repeat;*/
                            background: url('../../images/sistema/checkbox/checkbox-selected.png') no-repeat;
                        }

                        .custom-checkbox input[type="checkbox"] {
                            margin: 0;
                            position: absolute;
                            z-index: 2;
                            cursor: pointer;

                        }

                    /* Let's Beautify Our Form */
                    form {

                @*<script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.5.1.min.js"></script>*@
                <script>
                    function customCheckbox(checkboxName) {
                        var checkBox = $('input[name="' + checkboxName + '"]');
                        $(checkBox).each(function () {
                            $(this).wrap("<span class='custom-checkbox'></span>");
                            if ($(this).is(':checked')) {

                                $(this).parent().addClass("selected");

                            }
                        });
                        $(checkBox).click(function () {
                            $(this).parent().toggleClass("selected");
                        });
                    }
                    $(document).ready(function () {
                        customCheckbox("sport[]");
                        customCheckbox("car[]");
                        customCheckbox("confirm");
                    })

                            $('#btn_enviar_correo_recibo_pdf').attr('disabled', true);

                        }
                    });

                </script>

            @*https://moderncss.dev/pure-css-custom-checkbox-style/
              https://www.tutorialrepublic.com/codelab.php?topic=faq&file=custom-radio-buttons

            *@


            <style>
                /* The container */
                .chbx_container {
                    display: block;
                    position: relative;
                    padding-left: 35px;
                    margin-bottom: 12px;
                    left: -3px;
                    top: 5px;
                    cursor: pointer;
                    font-size: 16px;
                    -webkit-user-select: none;
                    -moz-user-select: none;
                    -ms-user-select: none;
                    user-select: none;
                }

                    /* Hide the browser's default checkbox */
                    .chbx_container input {
                        position: absolute;
                        opacity: 0;
                        cursor: pointer;
                        height: 0;
                        width: 0;
                    }

                /* Create a custom checkbox */
                .chbx_checkmark {
                    position: absolute;
                    top: 0;
                    left: 0;
                    height: 26px;
                    width: 26px;
                    border-radius: 50px;
                    background-color: #eee;
                    border: 2px solid #c9c9c9;
                }

                /* On mouse-over, add a grey background color */
                .chbx_container:hover input ~ .chbx_checkmark {
                    background-color: #ccc;
                }

                /* When the checkbox is checked, add a blue background */
                .chbx_container input:checked ~ .chbx_checkmark {
                    background-color: #2196F3;
                    border: 2px solid #c9c9c9;
                }

                /* Create the checkmark/indicator (hidden when not checked) */
                .chbx_checkmark:after {
                    content: "";
                    position: absolute;
                    display: none;
                }

                /* Show the checkmark when checked */
                .chbx_container input:checked ~ .chbx_checkmark:after {
                    display: block;

            function cogerValor() {

                if (str == "dos" || str == "two" || str == "2") { str = 2; }
